# Site build changelog

When you finish editing files under `site/src/` (races, ballot data, render, styles tied to new UI copy):

1. Read and follow `.cursor/skills/site-build-changelog/SKILL.md`.
2. Prepend the current session’s changes to `site/src/data/site-updates.ts`.
3. Set `BALLOT_META.lastContentUpdated` in `site/src/data/meta.ts` to the same `dateLabel`.

Do this in the same task as the feature—do not leave changelog updates for the user to request separately.
